{"title":"Kali Linux中安装Ibus拼音输入法","slug":"Kali_install_ibus","date":"2018-04-21T15:22:14.289Z","updated":"2018-04-22T14:03:19.296Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Kali_install_ibus.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"Ibus是GNU/Linux和UNIX操作系统下GPL协议分发源代码的开源免费语言输入法框架。<br>Kali Linux中默认是没有安装有中文输入法的。","covers":null,"content":"<p>Ibus是GNU/Linux和UNIX操作系统下GPL协议分发源代码的开源免费语言输入法框架。<br>Kali Linux中默认是没有安装有中文输入法的。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"Start-Terminal\"><a href=\"#Start-Terminal\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Start Terminal\"></a>Start Terminal</h2><h3 id=\"Command-line-Input\"><a href=\"#Command-line-Input\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Command-line Input\"></a>Command-line Input</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># apt-get install ibus</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Install-an-input-method\"><a href=\"#Install-an-input-method\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Install an input method\"></a>Install an input method</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">root@Crazy:~<span class=\"comment\"># apt-get install ibus-pinyin</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Finish\"><a href=\"#Finish\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Finish\"></a>Finish</h3><p>点击桌面右上角的设置-&gt;区域和语言，在输入源中添加汉语(拼音)</p>\n<h3 id=\"Restart\"><a href=\"#Restart\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Restart\"></a>Restart</h3><p>重启电脑，可通过Win+space切换输入法</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}